FBIS4-10140 "drlat068_a_94006" FBIS-LAT-94-068 Daily Report 6 Apr 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Antigua, Barbuda Establish Diplomatic Ties Antigua, Barbuda Establish Diplomatic Ties FL0704153194 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 2300 GMT 6 Apr 94 FL0704153194 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Spanish BFN [Text] On 6 April, documents were signed at Cuba's permanent UN mission ratifying the establishment of diplomatic relations between Cuba and the government of the islands of Antigua and Barbuda. In a brief address, Cuban UN Ambassador Fernando Remirez de Estenoz stated that this is of extreme importance if Cuba wishes to join the Caribbean community of peoples.
